headline: Why Enphase Energy Stock Was Sputtering This Week
summary: It's been a bad few days for renewable energy companies, particularly those that specialize in solar.  The past few trading days haven't been kind to solar energy stocks, and Enphase Energy (NASDAQ: ENPH) has been caught in the rout.  Developments in the legislative sphere kicked off the downturn, which was compounded in Enphase's case by several downbeat analyst notes.
